The kidnapped Sole Administrator of the Ideato North local government area of Imo State, Chris Ohizu, has been beheaded. Ohizu was kidnapped last week by the gunmen after his country home was razed down by the unknown assailants. In a video posted on Ohizu WhatsApp status early Monday morning, the gunmen were seen beheading Ohizu at a yet-to-be identified location. The gunmen, who spoke in Imo dialect, also sent out threats to the Imo State governor, Hope Uzodinma. Details Laterâ€¦